==Malayalam==
===Noun===
'''നാരങ്ങ''' [naːraŋːa]
#[[orange]] - this is seldom used nowadays, as most people just use the English word orange.
#[[lemon]] - the word is normally used in this sense. A more specific name is ചെറുനാരങ്ങ [ʈʃerunaːraŋːa], which literally means "small orange".
